tu.be%2F16CiwPChpr0&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=27b875e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0</a><br />\n<br />\n佢哋撤退埋之後，就成班白衣人推起大閘，再次攻入元朗站，無差別打到市民頭破血流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢隊警察睇裝束點睇都似雜牌軍，無個睇落好fit好揪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但如果當日佢哋肯留低保護市民，成件事都未必無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:02:03.000Z","msg":"你班人搞元朗踩到人哋地頭挑釁唔夠打 又想黑警幫手<br />\n真係好柒<br />\n雖然黑警係要調停<br />\n不過要幫你地啲黃絲廢柴真係陰功"},{"pid":"d7e5135f0b9845bcf44a35149b1e8e1fd0aa1a23","tid":2018132,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18abf60b4a3b97fd75cbbf727abcd74ac45cb8b0","tid":2018132,"uid":71822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c9d1aceb2bafce43f893d5cb7afb59ca04ae72","tid":2018132,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"601651063cde0cc294b8f5e908bb248a5e7c568c","tid":2018132,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:30:05.000Z","msg":"有無人知佢哋最後去咗邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6e97ed02591ef1a903f9a648b8d22c3ccd6015","tid":2018132,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94e2e1c51bdcc62d9714d65e3b56a0d8970e904c","tid":2018132,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a006af9422088374de6bf041026464f550190fc3","tid":2018132,"uid":61161,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KPxENw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn